 Reverse a String

Write a program to print the reverse of a given String.

The program should take a String as input and display the reversed version of that String.

Input Format

A single String.

Output Format

The reversed String.

Examples
Example 1
Input:
hello
Output:
olleh


import java.io.*;
void main(){
    String a = IO.readln();
    IO.print("Reversed String: ");
    for(int i=a.length()-1; i>=0; i--){
        IO.print(a.charAt(i));
    }
}


